Usage: ./server.sh -i <ip> -a <action> [-o <option>]
Actions:
- list        - list of all servers
- reboot      - reboot server [-o sw|hw|man]
- wol         - wake on lan server
- rescue      - boot server in rescue system
- setup       - setup system on server
- rdns        - set reverse DNS entry
- server_name - set server_name
